{
  "texts": [
    "These methodologies have been applied especially in the field of molecular optimization (69-71).",
    "• Transformer-based Models: Drawing inspiration from natural language models like BERT, transformers view molecules as sequences of tokens.",
    "These models typically employ a string based molecular representation.",
    "A notable example is ChemBERTa (72).",
    "Transformers have also shown utility in suggesting structural modifications during the optimization phases of drug design (73, 74)."
  ]
}